This is the server side of the distributed counting.
We use google app engine for hosting.

Here are few hints if you want to host a version of this app yourself:
1. Create an app engine account.
2. Cahnge 'application' attribute in 'app.yaml' file to the name of your application.
3. Download the python SDK.
4. Upload this directory using the command './appcfg.py update /path/to/dir' 